# Hospital Management System

This project is created using MySQL.

## 📂 Database Name
hospital_management

## 📊 Tables
1. Patient
   - patient_id (Primary Key)
   - name
   - age
   - gender
   - phone

2. Doctor
   - doctor_id (Primary Key)
   - name
   - specialization
   - phone

3. Appointment
   - appointment_id (Primary Key)
   - patient_id (Foreign Key)
   - doctor_id (Foreign Key)
   - date
   - time
   - status
   - reason

## 🔗 Relationships
- One Patient can have many Appointments
- One Doctor can have many Appointments

## 💡 Description
This system manages hospital data including patients, doctors, and appointments.
